title: Halloween Candy
subTitle: Spending her first Halloween alone after a recent divorce, a writer searches for inspiration from trick-or-treaters who come to her door. Unfortunately, the night becomes a nightmare when one visitor makes this Halloween one she will never forget.

title: A Knight's Tour
subTitle: In a post-apocalyptic world, J.D. and Henry try to develop a friendship in the midst of swirling suspicions.

title: Bored Games
subTitle: The rules go out the window for three couples riding out the apocalypse as their food supplies deplete and they play the game of ravenous hunger.

title: Meathook
subTitle: A traumatized final girl must confront her past and a new wave of killings with help from a true-crime podcaster.
